### Sys Admin API Smoke (use HTTP file in REST Client or VSCode)

@host = http://localhost:3000
@token = {{sysAdminToken}}

### Login
POST {{host}}/api/sys-admin/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "superadmin",
  "password": "SuperAdmin@2024!"
}

### Companies list
GET {{host}}/api/sys-admin/companies
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create company
POST {{host}}/api/sys-admin/companies
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Demo Corp",
  "code": "DEMO2025",
  "domain": "@demo.com"
}

### Pending admins
GET {{host}}/api/sys-admin/company-admins/pending
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Stats
GET {{host}}/api/sys-admin/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Activities
GET {{host}}/api/sys-admin/activities?limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Metrics
GET {{host}}/api/sys-admin/metrics
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

